# ── FitNest Client — Environment Variables ──────────────────────
#
# LOCAL DEV:
#   Do NOT set VITE_API_URL — leave it blank so Vite's proxy
#   forwards /api → http://localhost:5000 automatically.
#   Just run both servers: `npm run dev` (client) + `node server.js` (server)
#
# RENDER / PRODUCTION:
#   Set VITE_API_URL to your Render backend URL:
#   VITE_API_URL=https://your-backend.onrender.com/api
#
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-backend.onrender.com/api
